<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:08:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列的全日制托拉学生比犹太历史上任何时候都多。为什么这变得无法忍受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</link><description>正是因为《托拉》研究对我来说如此珍贵，所以我想保留它，但要做到这一点，我们必须打破当今的范式，即成千上万的人在犹太学院学习，享受大量的国家福利，但不加入劳动力或以色列国防军。我们需要一个新模型</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的草莓丰收曾经是丰收的象征，现在却是战争的另一个受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</link><description>自 1967 年以来，加沙人就以收获“红色黄金”草莓而自豪，草莓在加沙地带被称为“红色黄金”。现在，加沙北部约 40% 的耕地变成废墟，农民对未来感到担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</guid></item><item><title>“不要炫耀你的犹太复国主义”：以色列向穆斯林国家和欧洲电视网发出旅行警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</link><description>以色列国家安全委员会敦促以色列人避免前往土耳其、摩洛哥、埃及和约旦。它补充说，计划参加瑞典欧洲电视网或法国奥运会的以色列人应避免表现出“以色列”特征</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其的另一次选举意味着埃尔多安再次夺权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/another-election-in-turkey-means-another-erdogan-power-grab/0000018e-84ec-df27-adee-a6fe60080000</link><description>在土耳其，每次举行选举，该国就离成为一个有意义的民主国家又迈出了一步。本周末的地方选举看起来将延续惨淡的模式</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/another-election-in-turkey-means-another-erdogan-power-grab/0000018e-84ec-df27-adee-a6fe60080000</guid></item><item><title>法国将对在加沙犯下战争罪的法以士兵采取法律行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/france-to-take-legal-action-against-french-israeli-soldiers-involved-in-war-crimes-in-gaza/0000018e-8530-d0d3-a98e-d7ff169e0000</link><description>在左翼政党的压力下，外交部表示将对任何在加沙从事构成战争罪活动的双重国籍士兵采取法律行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/france-to-take-legal-action-against-french-israeli-soldiers-involved-in-war-crimes-in-gaza/0000018e-8530-d0d3-a98e-d7ff169e0000</guid></item><item><title>她的兄弟活埋了她：巴勒斯坦-以色列导演敢于批评名誉杀人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-story-about-a-palestinian-woman-who-was-buried-alive-but-survived/0000018e-7fd3-d669-a9fe-7fff0cd10000</link><description>出生于拿撒勒的巴勒斯坦导演谢迪·斯鲁尔在以色列电视台播出其酝酿已久的电视剧《Fadia》时，讲述了他为何拒绝对社会中女性被谋杀的事件保持沉默</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-story-about-a-palestinian-woman-who-was-buried-alive-