>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</link><description>在与总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡会面之前，被哈马斯扣押的以色列士兵的父母声称，内塔尼亚胡“只是在六个月的许多官方要求和媒体要求后才与以色列人会面”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学教授10月7日怀疑哈马斯性侵，后撤回原职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</link><description>巴勒斯坦学者 Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授在 10 月 7 日收回对哈马斯性侵犯程度表示怀疑的言论后，希伯来大学撤销了对她的停职。她没有被要求撤销关于以色列正在实施种族灭绝的说法在加沙</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周五早上开始实行夏令时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</link><description>夏令时将于周五凌晨 2 点生效</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:29:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤；以色列军队搜寻袭击者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-israeli-army-searching-for-assailant/0000018e-8435-df27-adee-a6ff9fc90000</link><descrip