，并驳回了卡布 (Kabub) 对他参与涉及其子女的法律纠纷审判的指控的回应。所有针对他的投诉都是由右翼活动家谢伊·格利克（Shay Glick）提交的</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡政府准备招募极端正统派入伍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</link><description>提交请求的截止日期已于周三午夜到期。如果不提交，内阁关于免除极端正统派男子征兵的决定将于周一到期，他们将被征召服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派兵役豁免危机对以色列政治来说是一个地震事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</link><description>即使本杰明·内塔尼亚胡未能通过一项免除所有犹太学院学生服兵役的法律，极端正统派政党也可能会留在政府，但在下一次选举后，他们可能会长期处于反对派状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:56:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯使以色列人失去人性。在以色列，巴勒斯坦人的处境严重非人化。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</link><description>参谋军士。 21 岁的尼西姆·卡奇隆 (Nisim Kachlon) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，在加沙地带南部与恐怖分子的战斗中身亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 18:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-combat/0000018e-8107-d0d3-a98e-d7ff33930000</guid></item></channel></rss>